1999;;A Slipping-Down Life;;American;;Toni Kalem;;Lili Taylor, Guy Pearce;;romance;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Slipping-Down_Life;;Shy loner Evie (Taylor) hears musician Drumstrings Casey (Pearce) on the radio one night and becomes infatuated with him. She pursues him, carving his name (sadly, backwards) in her forehead with broken glass, and eventually they meet and then marry. They both still struggle to make something of their lives.